{"tid":1258652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸海關查往香港貨車，唔可以有頭盔口罩手套嗰啲","createTime":"2019-06-26T08:11:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T14:08:48.000Z","uid":39752,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"49d743d780c934790c84110b37c003a07fcd6194","tid":1258652,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T08:11:44.000Z","msg":"[緊急突發]大陸海關即日至起7月1日通知<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/daLNtT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/daLNtT</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁係咪即係只要我有任何件報關寫「头盔」「口罩」「手套」「黑色T恤」「旗杆旗帜」「标语横幅」就一定會查車</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我就好誠實嘅，買一個口罩都會誠實報關<br />\n絕對唔會俾大陸海關查漏任何一架車</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過細聲提醒有嘢想買嘅巴打，非急用嘅話有好多外國勢力幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔使益大陸"},{"pid":"02ac744d12338b274f550f13beeb5d2cf28fbf8f","tid":1258652,"uid":35842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T08:12:48.000Z","msg":"驚到咁呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XQQREDk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXQQREDk.png&h=190dd71d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n2LmYZa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn2LmYZa.png&h=1855d90a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前立法局主席黃宏發踢爆：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">議事規則得撤回 押後 postpone or withdraw</span><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">冇暫緩</span></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/PrrEBU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/PrrEBU</a><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">(懶既直接係最底copy) </span></span></div><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cc0bee1e7f569ae8d922130d7d815af827ddda5","tid":1258652,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T08:15:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db6922e7e4db5e78493fc7805e3c044c4d5ab865","tid":1258652,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T08:16:28.000Z","msg":"Amazon集郵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"001d034e815cc84d517e848c659ce28912855baf","tid":1258652,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T08:19:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"792a82330e79554271e648cdd9cd536b3da192e2","tid":1258652,"uid":159307,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T08:20:21.000Z","msg":"個個買一件付運，頂鳩住啲關口"},{"pid":"16d607d91840531fdc532c4255a3b6c38caad94c","tid":1258652,"uid":39752,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"792a82330e79554271e648cdd9cd536b3da192e2","tid":1258652,"uid":159307,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T08:20:21.000Z","msg":"個個買一件付運，頂鳩住啲關口"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T08:26:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好唔鼓勵大家咁做，會阻住好多車，好多港豬拎唔到淘寶"},{"pid":"630b1fa623f531240d6b44e1fca4ecaee6425f95","tid":1258652,"uid":53604,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T08:36:56.000Z","msg":"超合作運動"},{"pid":"8e36ebb4974981ede6efaf689515ad5b4e148e8f","tid":1258652,"uid":61281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T08:39:15.000Z","msg":"大家做得好"},{"pid":"294fb2c829369baeed421e56958590d6384493f2","tid":1258652,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T09:13:33.00